title: Internet Download Manager 6.20 Build 1 Final
description:
Internet Download Manager - it is a tool to increase download speed, supports uploading and downloading on schedule.

New in version:
Improved video recognition in web players
Added the recognition and downloading of TS videos
Resolved "403 Forbidden" problems while downloading some videos
Fixed bugs

Installation:
1) Install and close program
2) copy idm.6.19.7.3-patch-unreal.exe to folder with installed program
3) Click PATCH, enter anything and click REG.

Interface language - English, Russian and others
